news_header: Murphy Oil will hold a conference call on January 30, 2025, to discuss Q4 24 earnings.
news_text: Murphy Oil (MUR) is set to host a conference call at 9:00 AM ET on January 30, 2025, to discuss its Q4 24 earnings results. Interested parties can access the live webcast at their investor relations website or listen by calling 800-717-1738 with Conference ID: 18687. The opinions expressed are those of the author and do not reflect Nasdaq, Inc.
